{"tid":1900451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國同WHO已經開始想spin“中國比西方安全”了","createTime":"2020-02-27T08:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T09:02:55.000Z","uid":228995,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6640623fe61bece5c4af255630643799999e4824","tid":1900451,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:32:20.000Z","msg":"作者<br />\n2 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n中共和世衛玩髒區轉移，一步一步找人接貨脫手病毒。譚德塞在兩星期前否認武漢肺炎會在全球大流行，前幾天卻轉口風叫各國做好準備；世衛專家反覆強調疫情在中國轉弱、境外轉強，無視中共捏造死亡和確診數字，還說全世界欠了武漢，幫中共打掃乾淨地方。昨天文宣部炒作「境外新增確診首度超過中國」，是為了塑造全世界比中國更髒，不用一個月，中共就可自信地說不安因素不再來自湖北，病毒是來自其他國家，轉移公敵之餘，也幫自己解套。<br />\n<br />\n這個星期，中共按步就班做這種政治操作。山東地方政府針對地方韓僑，禁止南韓人入境，是中共鋪張「病毒變成境外輸入」的第一步。現在，這個輸出病毒的國家，宣佈它第一宗輸入性個案。患者是一位寧夏老伯，2月19日從伊朗到達莫斯科，住了膠囊酒店後才搭飛機回上海，22日坐火車回到蘭州。這個公告，一來拆穿伊朗2月19日才爆疫的謊言，二來送大禮給普京，這樣對盟友真不錯。<br />\n<br />\n細節請看：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/34378099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F34378099&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=089748d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/34378099</a><br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n#金蟬脫疫<br />\n#不是你帶入伊朗的嗎"},{"pid":"0d94d3456834f95e5facb5e2740145d264420c44","tid":1900451,"uid":300435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"9月參選人立刻發動及宣傳政綱,削減驚方預算,慳返果D錢派比市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdtdPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdtdPS</a><br />\n<br />\n既然777無恥派錢,<br />\n我地都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻宣傳政綱,<br />\n9月立會一過半,<br />\n就即刻發動議案,<br />\n削減驚方預算，<br />\n<br />\n驚方1年預算258億元,<br />\n削減一半就130億元,<br />\n4年立法任期就520億元,<br />\n再叫政府比D錢來,<br />\n就儲夠710億,<br />\n下年又可以派一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d012862c5e4170ccdb4157d2adaa0e3a2f3338","tid":1900451,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:33:32.000Z","msg":"好安全<br />\n直接火化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超高溫消毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f478ce266ed1001a30a810962f05beb166ca04","tid":1900451,"uid":62512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:35:49.000Z","msg":"快D 開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29eb892b0ea3ab306450a6975a8c3fab92d3a919","tid":1900451,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"又想內部矛盾轉移到外部<br />\n咁只會加快國際同強國脫勾"},{"pid":"cde05b2bb2fc2a3a8ca91f947c9a9321b1ff9b9f","tid":1900451,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29eb892b0ea3ab306450a6975a8c3fab92d3a919","tid":1900451,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"又想內部矛盾轉移到外部<br />\n咁只會加快國際同強國脫勾"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"但西方國家奶支<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9251076d0f4be5019def85876e57c3a35f169b","tid":1900451,"uid":326017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cde05b2bb2fc2a3a8ca91f947c9a9321b1ff9b9f","tid":1900451,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29eb892b0ea3ab306450a6975a8c3fab92d3a919","tid":1900451,"uid":326017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"又想內部矛盾轉移到外部<br />\n咁只會加快國際同強國脫勾"},"citedB